## üöÄ Quick Start

### Create New Service
``````powershell
cd $baseDir\scripts
.\init-service.ps1 -ServiceType "web-backend" -ServiceName "payment-api" -Language "nodejs"
``````

### Work with Specific AI
``````powershell
# Use DeepSeek-R1 for architecture
