‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ web\                     # Web applications
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ frontend\            # React, Vue, Angular, etc.
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ backend\             # Node, Python, Go, etc.
